zoning district.
(6) The multifamily residential sign district includes land in the following zoning districts:
(a) townhouse and condominium residence (SF-6);
(b) multifamily residence limited density (MF-1);
(c) multifamily residence low density (MF-2);
(d) multifamily residence medium density (MF-3);
(e) multifamily residence moderate-high density (MF-4);
